OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny rain and
OL,6,Fheavy showers soon fading into the
OL,7,Fevening with clear spells developing.
OL,8,FCloud then thickens again from the
OL,9,Fwest after midnight, perhaps bringing
OL,10,Fone or two further showers, mainly to
OL,11,Fwestern areas. Breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FBreezy start with a mixture
OL,14,Fof sunny spells and showers,
OL,15,Foccasionally heavy. Winds will ease
OL,16,Fthrough the day, with showers also
OL,17,Ffading into the evening. Feeling warm
OL,18,Fin any sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
